thread.title: Scott

author: Scott
title: Scott
text: We had ordered several different kind of bushes from the company. Our blueberry bushes didn't come with the rest of the order and the company had me take pictures of my rows to prove I was telling the truth. The raspberry bushes they did send were dead, and they told us to ship them back. They also said they couldn't ship us good ones til the fall cause it was too late. We did finally get the good bushes in the fall, but with so many issues with our order, it is doubtful that we will be ordering from this company again.
